history.content:
Have you heard that your professor has started their 100th startup? Curious about how long hours of research can translate into a successful product? Come to the “Academia and Entrepreneurship” event to find out how they do it! Speak to various PhD students and professors about how work in their lab translated to working on a startup.

Join SWE's Startup Spring, ASUC Senator Sensurucu's Office, and M.E.T. this Wednesday 2/23, 4 to 5 PM at 120 Bechtel. RSVP here: https://forms.gle/tzV1ubaM2uZsa5iN8
history.subject: Join us for our Academia and Entrepreneurship Event Wed 2/23, 4 to 5 PM @ 120 Bechtel!
